### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@contentType = application/json

### =============================================================
### AUTH ENDPOINTS  (/api/auth)
### =============================================================

### [AUTH-1] Signup - Job Seeker (happy path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "phone": "+34600000001",
  "role": "ROLE_JOB_SEEKER"
}

###

### [AUTH-2] Signup - Employer (happy path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Acme Corp HR",
  "email": "hr@acme.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "phone": "+34600000002",
  "role": "ROLE_EMPLOYER"
}

###

### [AUTH-3] Signup - Admin role rejected (expect 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Bad Actor",
  "email": "admin.attempt@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "phone": "+34600000099",
  "role": "ROLE_ADMIN"
}

###

### [AUTH-4] Signup - Duplicate email (expect 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Jane Doe Again",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "phone": "+34600000001",
  "role": "ROLE_JOB_SEEKER"
}

###

### [AUTH-5] Signup - Missing required fields (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "no.name@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "ROLE_JOB_SEEKER"
}

###

### [AUTH-6] Login - Valid credentials (happy path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### [AUTH-7] Login - Wrong password (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### [AUTH-8] Login - Non-existent user (expect 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "ghost@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### [AUTH-9] Login - Invalid email format (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### =============================================================
### USER ENDPOINTS  (/api/v1/users)
### =============================================================

### [USER-1] Get own profile by email header (happy path)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
X-User-Email: jane.doe@example.com

###

### [USER-2] Get own profile - Non-existent user (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
X-User-Email: ghost@example.com

###

### [USER-3] Update own profile (happy path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-User-Email: jane.doe@example.com

{
  "fullName": "Jane Updated",
  "phone": "+34699999999",
  "profileImage": "https://example.com/avatar/jane.png"
}

###

### [USER-4] Update own profile - Non-existent user (expect 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-User-Email: ghost@example.com

{
  "fullName": "Ghost",
  "phone": "+34600000000",
  "profileImage": null
}

###

### [USER-5] Get user by ID (happy path — replace 1 with a real ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1

###

### [USER-6] Get user by ID - Not found (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/999999

###

### [USER-7] Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users

###

### [USER-8] Suspend user (replace 1 with a real ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1/suspend

###

### [USER-9] Activate user (replace 1 with a real ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1/activate

###

### [USER-10] Soft-delete user (replace 1 with a real ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1/delete

###

### [USER-11] Suspend non-existent user (expect 404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/999999/suspend

###
